        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="span5">
            <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uploads.hipchat.com/46883/314424/exovvpc26etcptp/icon_phone_16x16.png"
                 class="pull-left img-rounded">
            <p>
              <b>&nbsp;Have Questions?</b> Call us at 1 (855) 2-SPACES</p>
